{"tid":296373,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[影片後製] 一個好既廣告你可能唔知既野","createTime":"2017-06-24T13:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T13:01:47.000Z","uid":68124,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bc6d0e4fb0ca555ba14a6862c69e77873441a8","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"一個好睇既廣告，主角、劇本、剪接固然重要，<br />\n不過其實畫面亦佔著一個好重要既地位。<br />\n<br />\n事實上往往最容易被忽略既就係畫面上既後製。<br />\n<br />\n點解咁講呢？ <br />\n<br />\n小弟都叫做做左影片既後期製作幾年，對後製、<br />\n特效、動畫有少少研究。<br />\n<br />\n一般人睇到既電影、電視廣告甚至而家流行既網絡片<br />\n除左睇內容之外 ，最容易分別出既電腦特效同動畫<br />\n就係一D現實中唔會出現既野。<br />\n例如D魔法星塵飛飛下或者片頭片尾，片名等等，<br />\n不過其實就算現實會出現既野都有機會用到後製。<br />\n<br />\n我今次想講既係一般人未必會留意既後期製作<br />\n好多時廣告既要求比網絡片高好多(電影可能更高啦,<br />\n但因為廣告比較常見，所以先用廣告做例子)<br />\n<br />\n你未必會知, 廣告入面既人皮膚好左、瘦左、白左<br />\n甚至乎禿頭都變到有頭髮都係後製既功勞。<br />\n建築物既顏色、形狀、路牌都可能被後製師執過先出街。<br />\n其實咁做既目的在於你對條片有幾大既要求，<br />\n要求愈高既片，愈唔會想俾其他唔關事既畫面影響<br />\n劇本上既創作。自自然然更容易成為一個成功既廣告。<br />\n<br />\n簡單D講，其實同執相差唔多，只不過將相轉換成片<br />\n你可能會諗&ldquo;咁我識執相，做影片都一樣架姐&rdquo;<br />\n冇錯, 做既野係一樣 ，但做法會好唔同。<br />\n一般廣告25格一秒，電影24格一秒，<br />\n你冇可能每一秒都執25張相掛？<br />\n就算你肯做都未必做得快，尤其係香港呢d咁節奏急促既地方，<br />\n所以點樣有效率去做都係一種學問。<br />\n<br />\n當然點樣利用特效去加強創作上既表達、<br />\n文字既動畫去帶動觀眾既視點、<br />\n解決拍攝或成本上不能達到既效果、<br />\n美化畫面或令平凡既畫面變到生動有趣等等<br />\n都需要依靠後期製作。<br />\n<br />\n下篇會講下 [後期製作如何幫助影片創作]<br />\n<br />\n有咩想知或者有興趣可以交流下<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/User0000user\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUser0000user&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=13ca4482\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/User0000user</a>"},{"pid":"4ddc9d5986ff434083dd0f8a7c2c72916bee1f5a","tid":296373,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"留名學吓嘢"},{"pid":"9d3995bdc80a272267a7128fe336d53b7584d3bf","tid":296373,"uid":5275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e43a9614bbe8a0eb725fa745c2cb085917335f9a","tid":296373,"uid":36880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c608cc232a61039e06d9d0649584a11c2b061a6","tid":296373,"uid":94843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"90fc74766d8d041a6eae9e722b79d42cabc30b88","tid":296373,"uid":15950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:38:37.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"723df95594731151452a53a7edc11ccebec1916f","tid":296373,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:02:19.000Z","msg":"請唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ec2b3d529e8d6dafd95c4ee009d1c5133fef47","tid":296373,"uid":67507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d54256668439ad6f7c6e61a27bf30643c59a935f","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暫時未等人用"},{"pid":"c16e4aeab30adcfcd9fa8c3d341a19e01c26faa9","tid":296373,"uid":110218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"呢行D野難唔難學架？<br />\n有冇執過邊D明星好醜樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e858c69f76db31d80cf2435f3319853b9931210c","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢行D野難唔難學架？<br />\n有冇執過邊D明星好醜樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n技術野其實唔係佔好大部分<br />\n始終同一個效果 可以有唔同方法去做<br />\n難在要諗到一個方法 可以最快 最適合黎做<br />\n<br />\n基本上要求高少少既片 都會執過d樣先出街<br />\n唔少明星都好殘 眼袋黑眼圈 暗瘡 少不了<br />\n老既執下鄒紋 斑 頭髮果d"},{"pid":"c86d4465e7521a596f70f7a101dae3b39edc727b","tid":296373,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ea91bc2c8bc383763789966618be5c15bb602dd1","tid":296373,"uid":94843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"用啲咩軟件整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd15e636138e91425762b527fafc1f0d63a99895","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用啲咩軟件整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAfter Effect 會比較常用<br />\n如果要3d Element 3d CINEMA 4D maya 都會用到"},{"pid":"e29ed994dd58c18e9bfffdb80637ac87ed22e07e","tid":296373,"uid":67848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢 想學下特效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad9f9f7831cd339c86fa4dbf872e086ade2c992","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"[後期製作如何幫助影片創作]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創作影片，最重要當然係個idea啦，<br />\n一條好橋係直接決定條片好唔好睇既最大因素。<br />\n但你有冇試過諗左條好橋之後，發覺原來唔可行、<br />\nBudget唔夠、 拍攝上有困難、天氣因素等等<br />\n而放棄本身一條好好既橋。<br />\n<br />\n創作唔應該俾任何野規限住自己，<br />\n其實創作真係可以天馬行空,沒有限制。<br />\n<br />\n點解咁講呢？<br />\n因為基本上冇乜野係後製做唔到既，<br />\n只要有時間,加上現時既軟件同技術，再複雜既畫面<br />\n都可以靠後製呈現出黎。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝上既規限，最常見既有因器材入鏡既影響，<br />\n係狹窄既拍攝環境，往往無可避免燈腳、腳架、路軌等<br />\n於畫面中出現，而當唔影響畫面構圖下唯一可做的就是<br />\n後製將那些物品抺除。(強調一下，這裡是說因無可避免<br />\n既情況下，絕對不是為了方便而依賴後製。現實避免到的，<br />\n盡量也要於拍攝時避免)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外例如化妝品廣告，把模特兒皮膚變成雞蛋咁滑；<br />\n牙膏廣告，把模特兒的牙齒是變成白紙咁白；<br />\n健美廣告，把模特兒的體形變成S型般纖幼。<br />\n產品廣告，把產品的瑕疵抺除，突出產品等<br />\n都可以幫助廣告希望表達的訊息突顯出來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外還有天氣的規限，藍天白雲或烏雲密佈甚至下雨下雪<br />\n的要求也是無辦法去控制，如創作有這特定要求，<br />\n也可能需要到後製把天換調。<br />\n<br />\n還有物理上的限制，人和物在空中漂浮、水中呼吸、<br />\n太空中漫步。取景亦可能預到的問題，例如有一個<br />\n非常合適的戶外景，但當中有個公廁影響景觀，<br />\n把公廁換成另一樣建築物也不失為一個好方法。<br />\n<br />\n有了後製就可以減少受到種種因素而限制影響到創作，<br />\n當然時間及前期準備要非常充足才能把品質做好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下篇會講下 [如何有效率地去處理後期製作]<br />\n<br />\n有咩想知或者有興趣可以交流下<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/User0000user\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUser0000user&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=13ca4482\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/User0000user</a>"},{"pid":"66131fdd06afa34652ccb8f48260cfb457b0fabe","tid":296373,"uid":15817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:50:56.000Z","msg":"做邊間後期公司？"},{"pid":"d705790a9065debb4ebd12531cd0a6acbeba2ddd","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做邊間後期公司？</blockquote><br />\n唔自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f23193595c8993f4cd7b5488aa62cd3f6ae3f78","tid":296373,"uid":94843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用啲咩軟件整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAfter Effect 會比較常用<br />\n如果要3d Element 3d CINEMA 4D maya 都會用到</blockquote><br />\n如果想學整可以點學<br />\n你係點學番黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6fd70c3bfa74cd35df26b193ff4490f406e1bc","tid":296373,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8455e7be5f806037fb84651dd11276e8d21f5538","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用啲咩軟件整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAfter Effect 會比較常用<br />\n如果要3d Element 3d CINEMA 4D maya 都會用到</blockquote><br />\n如果想學整可以點學<br />\n你係點學番黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想學可以tg 我交流下<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/User0000user\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUser0000user&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=13ca4482\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/User0000user</a>"},{"pid":"e497c27137b54dbadeba93d403177437c714d059","tid":296373,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"點知自己有冇天份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d4b6cd4a03c0c60b72dbe127bd1620a964eb52","tid":296373,"uid":31359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"文案呢種職業難唔難搵？<br />\n入行要求高唔高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464e4c80e6132690ff28f4e08c529f3ca3cc626a","tid":296373,"uid":68124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點知自己有冇天份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你平時自己點樣處理問題<br />\n我自己覺得敢嘗試唔同方法解決同一件事既人比較優勢"},{"pid":"86a8b1f3d657399e9e12aae96011f9698dd443e2","tid":296373,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用啲咩軟件整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAfter Effect 會比較常用<br />\n如果要3d Element 3d CINEMA 4D maya 都會用到</blockquote><br />\n如果想學整可以點學<br />\n你係點學番黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nvideo copilot個啲都夠你用"}]}